Package Application.Residential

Class ResidentialApplicationRepo

java.lang.Object
Application.Residential.ResidentialApplicationRepo
All Implemented Interfaces:
ApplicationRepo<ResidentialApplication>
public class ResidentialApplicationRepo extends Object implements ApplicationRepo<ResidentialApplication>
Repository class for managing residential applications. Implements the ApplicationRepo interface and provides methods to store, retrieve, and filter residential applications using a HashMap data structure.
